  <div class="column_holder">
    <h1>
      <img alt="JOBS" src="/images/headers/pf_heading/dynamicimage.aspx?text=JOBS" />
    </h1>
    <div class="column_heading">
      <span id="ctl00_ContentPlaceHolder1_lblTop"><p>GRIN is constantly looking for talented people. All available positions are listed below. Apply via the form or by e-mail.  If you are interested in a position that isn&rsquo;t listed, please send your CV via e-mail to jobs@grin.se.</p></span></div>
    <div class="column_sep">
      <img src="img/jobs/jobs_open_sep.png" alt="Open positions" /></div>
    
    
      <div class="column_content">
        <h1>
          <img alt="Wednesday 04 February 2009" src="/images/headers/pf_small/dynamicimage.aspx?text=Wednesday 04 February 2009" />
        </h1>
        <h2>
          <img alt="Producer, Technology Group" src="/images/headers/pf_heading/dynamicimage.aspx?text=Producer, Technology Group" />
        </h2>
        <p>
          <span id="ctl00_ContentPlaceHolder1_lblJobText"><p>At GRIN, the core engine technology is shared across all games and all platforms. The engine and tools are created by a small team of dedicated and highly technical programmers. <br />
<br />
As a producer for the technology group your task will be to coordinate the requests from our different games, platforms and technology partners, and see to it that the work of the team proceeds in an orderly and structured way. You will track the feature development and ensure that all games are able to hit their deadlines. <br />
<br />
<strong>For this position we are looking for a person with </strong><br />
- Experience of project management<br />
- Excellent communication skills<br />
- Ability to make hard and smart decisions and take responsibility for them<br />
- Some programming background -- you don't need to be a &quot;star programmer&quot;, but you should know what programming is about and the challenges that face large scale programming projects <br />
<br />
Apply via <a href="mailto:ep@grin.se?subject=Producer%2C%20Technology%20Group">ep@grin.se</a>.</p></span></p>
      </div>
      <div class="column_nav">
        <span class="column_nav_cat">Contact</span>
        <p>
          Please send your application through the online form below, or by regular mail to
          our physical adress. If you prefer to send your application by email click
          <a href="&#109;&#97;&#105;&#108;&#116;&#111;&#58;&#101;&#112;&#64;&#103;&#114;&#105;&#110;&#46;&#115;&#101;">here</a>.</p>
